---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="News & Insights | Brenkley Doctoral College" description="The latest news, research insights, and thought leadership from Brenkley Doctoral College faculty and researchers.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-surface border-b border-border py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="section-label mb-4">News &amp; Insights</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">From the Brenkley Doctoral College Research Community</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">Articles, perspectives, and research insights from Brenkley Doctoral College faculty. Covering management research, doctoral education, and the future of professional scholarship.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Articles -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-1 gap-8">

        <!-- Article 1 -->
        <article class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Director's Dispatch</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-muted">14 April 2026</span>
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">
                <a href="/news/director-dispatch-research-worth-doing" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">What management research is actually worth doing in 2026</a>
              </h2>
              <p class="text-muted mb-4">The management research landscape is vast, fragmented, and uneven in its quality and relevance. Prof. Stanley Oliver argues that practitioner-researchers have a unique opportunity — and responsibility — to ask the questions that academic researchers cannot or will not.</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-muted">
                <span>By <strong>Prof. Stanley Oliver</strong></span>
                <span>&bull;</span>
                <span>7 min read</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border">
            <a href="/news/director-dispatch-research-worth-doing" class="btn-outline text-sm">Read article</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Article 2 -->
        <article class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <span class="tag tag-doctoral">Research Trends</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-muted">2 March 2026</span>
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">
                <a href="/news/executive-research-emerging-trends" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Executive Research: Emerging Trends Shaping Doctoral Inquiry in 2026</a>
              </h2>
              <p class="text-muted mb-4">From AI governance to climate-resilient leadership, the research questions attracting senior executives to doctoral study are changing. Prof. Stanley Oliver maps five trends that are reshaping the doctoral research agenda for practitioner-scholars in 2026.</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-muted">
                <span>By <strong>Prof. Stanley Oliver</strong></span>
                <span>&bull;</span>
                <span>8 min read</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border">
            <a href="/news/executive-research-emerging-trends" class="btn-outline text-sm">Read article</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Article 3 -->
        <article class="card">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                <span class="tag tag-training">Research Methods</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-muted">18 January 2026</span>
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">
                <a href="/news/emerging-management-research-areas" class="hover:text-accent transition-colors">Seven Emerging Management Research Areas Our Supervisors Are Watching</a>
              </h2>
              <p class="text-muted mb-4">Brenkley Doctoral College's supervisors are positioned at the intersection of academic research and professional practice. Prof. Stanley Oliver shares seven management research areas gaining significant traction among doctoral researchers and why they matter for organisations now.</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-muted">
                <span>By <strong>Prof. Stanley Oliver</strong></span>
                <span>&bull;</span>
                <span>9 min read</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border">
            <a href="/news/emerging-management-research-areas" class="btn-outline text-sm">Read article</a>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-surface border-t border-border py-16 px-6 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Join the research conversation</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">Brenkley Doctoral College researchers contribute to live debates in management, education, and organisational practice. Explore our programmes or connect with our faculty.</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap">
        <a href="/programmes" class="btn-primary">Explore programmes</a>
        <a href="/supervisors" class="btn-outline">Meet the team</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
